citations.desc: ACCESS AND INSPECTION OF RECORDS AND PROPERTY; SUBMISSION OF ITINERARIES.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 11:30 on
05-JUN-18.
The Inspector was able to make contact with the Licensee's wife. She confirmed that no one was available for
inspection at that time.
